---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Lucas Wang">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12 md:py-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black tracking-tight mb-8">About Me</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        I am a Senior Platform Engineer with 13 years of experience building secure, scalable production systems. 
        I specialize in cloud infrastructure, observability, CI/CD automation, and incident response.
      </p>
      
      <p class="mb-6">
        Throughout my career, I have led cross-domain projects encompassing infrastructure, observability, and security with a primary goal of improving the developer experience. I am passionate about building fault-tolerant, self-healing platforms that are intuitive to use, deploy, and operate.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">Core Expertise</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">Platform & Infrastructure</h3>
          <p class="text-sm">AWS, Kubernetes, AWS CDK, Terraform, Cloudflare, Akamai</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">Observability</h3>
          <p class="text-sm">Prometheus, Grafana, ELK, New Relic, Datadog, OpenTelemetry</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">CI/CD & DevEx</h3>
          <p class="text-sm">GitLab, Buildkite, GitHub Actions, Argo CD, Backstage</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">Security & Quality</h3>
          <p class="text-sm">Orca, CrowdStrike, SonarQube, Snyk, SOC 2 Compliance</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">Professional Philosophy</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        I believe in "shifting left" whenever possible—integrating security, quality, and observability directly into the platform pipelines. My focus is on enabling product teams to deploy independently and reliably through robust GitOps workflows and automated self-service platforms.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        Currently based in Adelaide, Australia, I continue to explore the intersection of distributed systems, AI-assisted development, and high-performance frontend architectures.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
